'''SSh-68鋼盔'''（{{lang-ru|'''Стальной шлем образца 1968 года'''}}，簡稱：'''СШ-68'''）是[[蘇聯軍隊|蘇聯軍隊]]曾經裝備的制式戰鬥頭盔，它是由{{tsl|en|SSh-60}}鋼盔進一步發展而來。與SSh-60相比，SSh-68主要提升了盔殼的強度，盔頂的弧度更呈傾斜，而且外部邊緣較短<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ultimatehistoryproject.com/headstrong.html |title=Ultimate History Project |access-date=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2020-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221031832/http://ultimatehistoryproject.com/headstrong.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大部份SSh-68都使用深綠色塗裝<ref>[www.bratishka.ru/archiv/2009/6/2009_6_14.php Sergey Monetchikov. Uniforms: From helmet to the steel helmet Magazine "Big Brother», № 6, June 2009 ]</ref>，每個頭盔重約1,300克，它們能夠保護佩戴者的頭部免受一般衝擊（如[[開山刀|開山刀]]的砍劈）所傷，也對以250米／秒的速度飛來的1克重碎片具備防禦效果<ref>[{{Cite web |url=http://www.popmech.ru/article/1197-chugunnyiy-lob/page/1/ |title=Dmitri Mamontov. Cast iron forehead: Keep your head "Popular Mechanics", February 2007  {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010062140/http://www.popmech.ru/article/1197-chugunnyiy-lob/page/1/ |date=2013-10-10 }} |accessdate=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010062140/http://www.popmech.ru/article/1197-chugunnyiy-lob/page/1/ |dead-url=no }} Dmitri Mamontov. Cast iron forehead: Keep your head "Popular Mechanics", February 2007  {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010062140/http://www.popmech.ru/article/1197-chugunnyiy-lob/page/1/ |date=2013-10-10 }}]</ref>。然而，由於SSh-68的定位並非防彈盔，故無法保證其能否阻擋子彈的衝擊。

除蘇聯自用以外，SSh-68還被大量出口，許多前[[華沙條約|華沙條約]]成員國及[[第三世界國家|第三世界國家]]皆有採用。直至今天，SSh-68仍舊為部份前蘇聯繼承國、[[越南|越南]]、[[北韓|北韓]]和[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]等國家的制式裝備<ref name="ICH">{{Cite web |url=https://www.militarytrader.com/militaria-collectibles/from-behind-the-iron-curtain-communist-bloc-helmets |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2022-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209095339/https://www.militarytrader.com/militaria-collectibles/from-behind-the-iron-curtain-communist-bloc-helmets |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

而在俄羅斯，SSh-68已大量被6B7-1M和[[6B47頭盔|6B47]]等新型頭盔取代。

